[DhtmlXQ_comment13_12]四局；[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_12]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13_15]正着。[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_15]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13_17]兑炮后，红车牵制黑右翼车马，仍持先手。[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_17]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13_20]黑平炮兑车，虽然损失一步棋，但使右马生根，卒林车便有活动余地。[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_20]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13_21]退车准备移右攻黑弱马，正确。[/DhtmlXQ_comment13_21]
