[DhtmlXQ_comment15_21]五局：[/DhtmlXQ_comment15_21]
[DhtmlXQ_comment15_25]红进一步车似笨实巧，待黑补士自塞马路，然后再退车运右翼攻击。[/DhtmlXQ_comment15_25]
[DhtmlXQ_comment15_26]弃卒通马路。[/DhtmlXQ_comment15_26]
[DhtmlXQ_comment15_28]红多兵略优。[/DhtmlXQ_comment15_28]
